House.S08.Special-Swan.Song.720p.HDTV.x264-BAJSKORV
Airdate 2012.05.21

A one-hour retrospective special that will look 
back at this groundbreaking, seminal series and 
feature interviews with the series' stars and 
producers, special original content and other 
surprises.

A lot of footage exhibits ghosting and such
where they converted 30fps and others to match 
the show footage at 24.

-TEAM BAJSKORV
